question: What is Pemetrexed's mechanism of action on GART?
cypher:
MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Pemetrexed')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Pemetrexed'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Pemetrexed')
)
  AND (
    toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('GART')
    OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('GART'))
  )
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 100

WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('MEK Inhibitor GDC-0623')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('MEK Inhibitor GDC-0623'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('MEK Inhibitor GDC-0623')
)
  AND (
    toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('MAP2K1')
    OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('MAP2K1'))
  )
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 100

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('Pilaralisib')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('Pilaralisib'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('Pilaralisib')
)
  AND (
    toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('PIK3R2')
    OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('PIK3R2'))
  )
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 100

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('C-Met Inhibitor')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('C-Met Inhibitor'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('C-Met Inhibitor')
)
  AND (
    toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('FLT1')
    OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('FLT1'))
  )
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 100

MATCH (t:Therapy)-[r:TARGETS]->(g:Gene)
WHERE (
  toLower(t.name) = toLower('PSI')
  OR any(s IN coalesce(t.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('PSI'))
  OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS toLower('PSI')
)
  AND (
    toLower(g.symbol) = toLower('HTR2A')
    OR any(s IN coalesce(g.synonyms, []) WHERE toLower(s) = toLower('HTR2A'))
  )
RETURN
  g.symbol AS gene_symbol,
  t.name AS therapy_name,
  r.moa AS targets_moa,
  coalesce(r.ref_sources, []) AS ref_sources,
  coalesce(r.ref_ids, []) AS ref_ids,
  coalesce(r.ref_urls, []) AS ref_urls
LIMIT 100
